@startuml svc-reservations--post-reservations-reservation_id-participants

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #2E86AB
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4F8
    LifeLineBorderColor #A23B72
    BoxBorderColor #F18F01
    BoxBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
    NoteBorderColor #c77b30
    NoteBackgroundColor #FEF3E7
}

title POST /reservations/{reservation_id}/participants\nAdd a participant to a reservation

participant "Client" as Client
participant "API Gateway" as GW #DBEAFE
participant "svc-reservations" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-reservations/]] #E8F4F8
participant "Guest Profiles" as GP [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/]] #FFF8F0
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #FCE4EC

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-reservations.html#/Reservations/addParticipant View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /reservations/{reservation_id}/participants
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : [[/microservices/svc-reservations/#post-reservationsreservation_idparticipants-add-a-participant-to-a-reservation route request]]
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> GP : [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/#get-guestsguest_id-get-guest-profile Validate participant]]
activate GP #DBEAFE
GP --> Svc : OK
deactivate GP

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : SELECT parent WHERE id = ?
activate DB #FCE4EC
DB --> Svc : Parent row
deactivate DB
note right of DB : 404 if parent not found

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FCE4EC
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml